      "content": "That makes sense, thanks for clarifying. It sounds incredibly risky for someone just working for themselves. \n\nAre there any specific \"red flags\" or certain words in an indemnification clause that I should look out for to know if a client is being particularly predatory or trying to hide something sneaky in the fine print?",
